data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom single family residence, constructed in 2018, seamlessly blends modern design with the tranquility of a picturesque water view. Step inside and be captivated by the contemporary elegance this home exudes. The property features 2 living spaces for easy entertainment. The kitchen, equipped with modern appliances, is a culinary enthusiast's delight. Each bedroom is a haven of comfort, providing ample space for relaxation and personalization. The allure of this home extends beyond its interiors. Imagine waking up to the gentle ripple of water, visible from your own backyard. Whether it's enjoying morning coffee on the upgraded patio or hosting gatherings with friends and family, the water view adds a touch of serenity to your outdoor living experience. Situated in a beautiful neighborhood, that offers a community pool and park, perfect for families. Conveniently located near schools, shopping and dining. Call today!
